allñapa' serrpare'tyeset époet pa'knor
ranto époet yerr awanmoet poetsatho o'ch e'nyeneta' anapoets
yapa' attha nanak yokwen o'ch pewapaterr achama' phañapa' awo't attha o' peshoranom o't
kowenat yemhñot
thorreñets
yomchanat allempo'ch ye'morrechá yemhño'ch ñeth morrechena yeyóm allempó o'ch ye'morrecha yamha
yenweñ yapxherrer epay yeyom o'ch yetsotsayes ñeth poktetsa allpon emñotets orat ñeth yapoktaten ñerra'm yotwapa eñech yetsotach
atarr sherbeney ñeth atarr poerets
pha'ñema't añ kellek allothpa' péchme'tyes pa'namen peñets
pékellka'nem pa'tatstato
yeserrpare't attho yeshomemhtena oñoth yeserrpare't atthó yekwampen pa'namen kakaxhno
pha'ñema'terrerr alla kellek allothpa' phanáp a'phtho'teñets esempo't sherbe'so'tenet
eso'cha' akellkar nekellka' arrcha' pékellka' ñanom
yeyexhkaten atontateñets ñamha chetampeñets yechme'tnen ñamha yenten atthekma'tets shonteñets
po'ñoxh napa' amá acheñeñó napa' wathrenan añ nomñene' yompor partsesha' atthoch neyxhaterres tarwasats
petsotsa koñeth serrparñats
errothena't orrtena soyamets
tharro'mar allothpa' o'ch yórenet poenaremh
atthekma'cha' mam nare't ñerra'm parant
errpona't rrarets na'nom páthe'tets a'yapaxho
photnom esthe' tsotstat orrtetsa all amá etampesnomo kellkarrom
thépa o'ch pho'ch peyém añema'tonapépa' poeserrparña ñeth kellkawa
eso't orrtaten añ apotheñets
allempo seserrparetwa sañema't añ kellek
tharro'mar amo' matsaye' aneno ñétho'mar e'moeñeto' all enáre'ten womenk oten
allempo yémtañe'chen moetañe'chen moetañe'chen tho' pa'tko
yapoktach esempo'ch yewañe eñótañ ñách moechatsete ñeth orrtaterre sankawarero
abrell temenk errpona't yeth échen árrorr abrell
esesha'the' yamots serrpárets añ akellkarethó eso'marthe kellkët añ yekellkayeswa ñamha yañema'twa serrparñatspa o'ch alla yeserrpareterr epay ayxhatañ ñamha yeyomnesha' allempo'ch yañema'ten
thepa' o'ch pétsotse péyochach ñeth yépene' ñerra'm ñeñth kak yerra' allothpa' o'ch peserrpare't épaph peyem eso'mathe' nanak sheben o'ch yame'ña ñamha o'ch yethore'ta ñerra'm choyoy
o'ch nañema't añ kellek añekop
ekothena'pa' ñó allsénsareth atthoch ama ya'rromñáthtenañe
allempoña ontet atethpa' awo'xho yeterret o'ch e'neret paknor tharro'mar ñapa' nanako' moerenanet allempoñapa' awo'xho yeterret awo' chope'cherret atomatpa' awo'xho xherret
atthoch yanen kowen yapoktatar allempo yapxhena
añ kellkë o's yañemater kellek allothpa' yanap a'phtho'teñe'ts
napa' o'ch nañema't añ kellek
llechap ñeth abllesa'tañ waserr ñeth emása'wa abllepoeñ chets ñeth amre't abell a'bexhen
añemat serrpare'tatas mamthoth
esokopthe sherben yanetsro
yekwayerr ñeth yekellkawanom
ora ñeñth yarrotampenaya ya'netsropa' añ yápoe' yáto' pártsesha' ñeñtho'mar añ poktetsa o'ch yekwamperr atthoch amach yechenkërro ama't awathaña
planta pa'llerrpa' kampoenan poésheñarr atsnañeth
eñe' all yéna'nen éppoxh ñamha poxh
esempo separtenapa' awathekma'ch se'manena o'ch awa'moenes keñkewash
yáphthotyes yamotsnesha ayxhatañ yeyomnésha errothenthe yépen pathetets yenaremh
ellerro shoranom patherr tsepenan teropexh
amách sépso náyese kellek atarr ñamha epoxh
phanap a'ptho'teñets ateth orrtena yethñats arrorr
karawa' pátherr karawatholl e'ñe eñótan ña' e'ñe nésochena
escha' socha' kellek
xharempeñet all amostena
okanesha'pa' échenane't poekañther
ror échenan kañther páthe'tets e'chorrenan toñerochemh
yapa' yéchen pa'namen páreshemaxhno allo yepartena
petma'ntach apko'meto
phokwa' chekmats ñeth ateth orretyetsa pa'tatscheto
poxh yéneñ allempó yamesen mame
acha'wanemh
pho'ch peyom o'ch a'ñema'tan peserrparña allempo o'ch akowenetnomh ñeth ama kowen nephayeso
awo'xho' awanmoet kornesheshó ñañapa'awo' otanet
amach a'ñemateña'pa' phanap añ a'phtho'tyeñets
yempoen o'ch yeñoch ñethcha' yexhatey kellek
tse'm rra'yenan ñeth poetsets
allo' nanak onare'tnena
petso'tse x anapoeñets eñe' pokte' serrparñatso' erro'thenat pa'moer koñewo' eso't achpoeth koñewo' atarrthe moparr koñewo' phaphthot eso'marthe' petso'tse
allempo cheshanesha enwoe yaphtho'terr eseshat moenene enwan añ serrparñats
amhchatareth o'ch all yañema'terrerr serrparñats
erra'the' yexhkatenet panmet
allempo ya'ñematwa kellek petsotsé x all poktena allothpa' peñotatey eso'marthé petsotsé all
yetmantach yekellkë apothenet attho yeyorayen alló yeyexhkatyen amách yeserrpare'tena
palltena shetamoets ñethcha' ya'nom
eso't pha'yen yamo'tsesha' eso'mare't nanak sherben o'ch ya'kra' poértsoxhnó eso't narmetser chopoets sánetsro' eso't narmetser ama chepoetso sa'netsro
ne'ñape'ch pa'thepho ro'këph
errpona'ch xhop échen the' pepe
all poen ñetha koñeth kothapñats ñeth eñotatnomoey pátherr llollo ñeth atarr atarwasañ yeñorayesa all yañema'tyen
phokthapeth patherr apotheñets ñeth phomneñ o'ch yetpatamech errothencha yeñora ñethcha' yapotha
kompreshchetholl poe'llomer
ror échenan pátherr papoé moneñ o'ch koyan poeyom yerr páthe'tets
petma'ntat tsotsmet ateth orretyena páthe'tets
xho'ch chaka'nom poetákër e'ñoch etaphsey yemokro ñeñthoch moeka'tsyepe' ñerra'm ateth yexhopo'tpa' amach ye'ñwo tharrro'mar máchayóto'ch yatsna't ñerra'm ama nanak kowemperryetopa' awo'ch xho' pha'pontserra
eso't ortetsa atma'ntataretho
machko'marnesha' añ yoten ñeth yamo'ts yexhetsa anets machko
se'tmantat pa'parexhno allempó sanap a'phtho'teñets
o'ch yent allpón thothe' topoena épo'mar pamp
esempothé phorrtat ñeth oten añ kowenchá phamothtenom
ottatsñats awanena othexhno po'mayo
phañema't kellek pa'socheñ petsotse all poktena
attho' kowameteñet amo' werro
o'ch eñótatyet errothenthe' yexhkatenet ñamha attho sherbeney sheperr
yeserrpare't esthe' yexhkaten yamots allo'ch yoran poenaremh
añ kellekpa' yexhateney atthoch yemoerannata
attho yokwampen all yexha'yena kakaxhno o'ch yeñema't patherr eñótateñets
a'poktatareth ñoñets esokopthe' sherben
eso'marthe' amá pokteyaye o'ch yexhoña mam ellerroneth
topo'mh rren panamen othexhno topateñets
petma'ntat ñeth palltetsa
allempo yérrothe'ten
peyenpoe' orrtate' cheta'teñtso ñeth rra'nom
errathe' amátsetenet
allothpa' entan atma'ntat pa'tatsmet ateth kellka'nom
tsapoñapa awo't wa'pa chos rrenana ora ñeth nanerret popoer
nerra'm esempo senatena epayech eñosesare'teññañet pothapor
atthekmo'ch pena
pe'nanom all poktena arr chetatsó napa o'ch nekellka pátherr serrparñats añekop arr yenetsro
eso't phokthapechen ñeth orrtetsa atman'tatarethó yekellkën ñeth kowen yent atman'tatarethó o'ch alla yanapoerrerr pathettsokma añ aphthoteñets
noxhpa' shoshnenan mash allóch yéma'tana pa'yey
tsotse' ñeth apoxhamexhno añekop yesherbhateñ allempo serrpare'tatannenet
enwet shetamoets o'ch éxhomoet atto'ch orrtá kowen
eso't pe'th yatañnesha' atthó etsotete'th tsách
thaññapa' awo' alla komraterranerr poe'llappa' awo'xho' erret époet ach ñamha mashokeñ e'ño' allpona chope'cherretpa' allepa'to'ch entwereterr ma'yarr all konkorpatse'tena komrame'tatsa thoño
serrparetateñetspa eñotoxhencha' yeserrparen
añ a'phthoteñets ñethcha' peyenpoe atethchá' pekellka
yoten esempo torereten shonker
yeñoten yénen amnar o'rrerr ñerra'm eñall yechme'ten po'poñ ñoñets ñeñth mone' atthema'thtetsa
phokthapech eso'kopthe' kellkët añ kellek ñeth sañematwa
pekwa'nem x x x x shontoche'tats ñeth yépha'wanom sochena a'yapaxhe'tets
errothenchá napoktatwa kellkëñets ñeth nakowentewá o'ch nekellka pa'mothroth neserrpareñ sochñets orrteñets moth phamothteñ awathpá allem po parrochpá rroxh yenayes attho allothñapa' o'ch
patherr patherr ametheñe'ts
yokwa'nom po'poñoneth
nomneñ o'ch negáterreph pa'namen epéxhno ñeñth nechme'tyen tharro'mar esempó nechenkënapa' ñeñthcha' pegáter ne'ñarnesha' ñañapa' amo' ame'ñano popapar parrochñapa' thósen awo' awo' eñótentsopawo xhepa'toch epotaph ashapell thoño awo'xho' alla poerrerra pa'pakllo amo' entwerrano popapar
yapa cheshotheñ eñótatarethey atthoch kowen yakoshen amách esoye' petmantat esthe' kowen pent ateth oten tho' yeyenpannena allempo yeyorayen yenarmexhno yeserrpare't épay yeyom allempopa yanap a'phtho'teñets
wa'nmer ñeth poerrar pen remosh
escha' sellkate' saphthoch ayxhatañ peyellsheñe'ch épaph peyomnesha' yechope'chnom xhapoeñets pemata phopoerrerra phames phopoerrerra pewapore'ch epsheña yellsheñe'chets
rrara'nom komonach
e'ñe poesheña'ttsoy ñeñthey yaneshaypa' xhothe' yethorrerrapañ eñoranataya yakñe'thar e'ñe yeñoñokmañen
a'bexhoten
yeserrpare't attho yépen aphthoteñets ñamha errothencha yapothayes
yerr monenan o'ch tsorran tokoyo alloch e'tampsan tsachtat
amach nanak pemtsana'tatsto ma'ñorr the'ta orrtennapha pamo'mte' ñañapa' awo' anápan pa'go' napá ama nemhcha'teñe mañorr pompor awo' xho' awenerr poetsatho
xhach e'morrtena ayotheñ eñore'retyetsa a'yomar
peye' narmetsoxhno allothpa' petsotsé x yeyo'cha'yes atma'ntatareth ñeth tsomtetsa ñanom
asollesopa' eñall oñsas ñeth sochetsa ñe'gas
phokwa'nom pa'namen topamets ñeth yechme'ten petpa' otatso chekmats ñeth kellkëtsa
okanesha sapo'marpa ateshamrrare poenarmexhno ama tama berroyaye
moenatenen ach neyorepato ñeth koyanesha' nanak moenenan nethapor o'ch rran kak
thomxhenet anorrxhenet yenam amách ñeth yomchanaten all wañen serrparñats
ayxhatañpa' o'ch otan cheshanesha' e'ñech kowen ame'ñet allcha' yentena ateth a'koshen ach ayxhatañpa' o'ch a'phthotan cheshanesha' erróthena't a'koshen ach
apoktatareth ametheñets onañché b
allempo tepoenet ñeth nanak apapa' arr sen poetsatho bhaxhayo
llollopa' ellerro tomatan poekoyen mapyo
petsorramhpes allothpa' o'ch pechte pa'tatstato ateth rromoenet kak po'poñ anetso
athasath shelle'taph shoteñets eso'marthe' kellkët añ kellek cheme'tateñets
ora allowen ta'te' tsach apexhrexh ñeth enañare' pajor meropa' nanakcha' agoreth
pekellka pekellkarmo ñamha all palltena atsotsareth
allempopa' ellapenethcha' atsnomoets amach tama wáteno
eso't senten arr atma'ntátarethó esthe' pha'yenet
echenanthe pa'cheñer añ kellkëñets
allempo partenet shomemtametspa'amach moeneto epoet poethapor añpa' añekop peñet atthoch e'ñech kowen atsepenet alló partenet tharro'mar theta attha moshnenet
apapa' apxhenan tsach pokollo
chetsoth
eso'marcha' phañemach
atthepach seperra samha atthothpa' amathe sapenkaterrno sokthapecher ñeth serrpare'tatwas eñótañ sekellkërr ñeth kowen sentyes
allempo rromoenét pa'nameño atthoch amá tháko'reto
poktethé' penteñ o'ch pechmeterr pa'parexhno
llollopa' pomotenpa' xha tasanom pothenotaph
e'mareteñets tserroth sabar jonyem yeñótaten ñeth yeyexhkaten
yap pátherr poeynañ teno'mar
petsotse chocro x ñeñth pathrro'tsen ñamha ñeñth ma'potsen
petma'ntát épa pa'par senare'ten ñamha ñeñth pechme't allothpa' o'ch péyasoch ellopa' o'ch penoñ pa'socheñ nésochena
páthetets a'metheñets echyenan ñeth kellkë eseshát otéts paxharr
aspan allempo yonnatapnateñ sashepan neñachorpa' onnatapnatenan aspan pa'pakllo
eso't eñótateneyña poeserrpareñ ekothena' ñeñth pha'yeñets
e'ñe pa'mothrothpa' eño' aña korratse'th yáto' parets epoet pa'mo'nasheñ yáto' koros ñamha po'xh yaknor apoekoya poesheña'tetspa' echyeneto'ch poeyochresha' yáto' paretspa' xhoch yexhkatanatenan pa'namen ñeth eñall añeñpo ateth ñerram
oten tho' serrparñatspa' añ eñótateney a'ttho korra'yese'th yamo'tsesha awath ñeth eñótaterrey yátañnesha' allcha'ña kothape'chatenyet atethcha' yokrra a'tthoch yeñótnoma a'tthoch yokwen yewomhcheña atthoch yemorrentannena allochñapa' e'ñech kowen ye'ñwena errponowañen
yeyoren pa'namen arrapo' poetsathoth ñeth ora yeyoren ñethpa' yató parets poeyexhkatar ñá athoré' ora pa'namen arrapo
poktethé yenareterr tsach ñeth metets
kokllomh mallamh poechñemh ñamha teñerochemh
pa'rrochñapa' machayotho' entan poesheñarr acheñ awo' sewosa ñethpa' añepa'to sochena kok ñapa nanako'ch tepoeñ ateth goten ñapaxho' atthoch pena
phokwa' añ átma'ntatareth allothpa' pékellka' a'poxhe' noñets
esesha't pathrrótsen
yapxha'nen kellkëñets yokwa'nen ñeth yepha'yen ora yeth yeyexhkatnen atma'ntat tsotstat
attho pemorrentenna
ateth yeshomemtena añeñpo sherbenthe yamotsokop ñamha popotantañokop
sañema't añ kellek allothpa' seserrparet
amach yañema'tena serrparñats o'ch yekellkayes kellkato ñethcha' yeyerpaterre cherra
pallerr ramoesh ñethcha' yorrtat ñanom
eso'marthe' a'mata'tat mhorr ora mammaxhno
all amhratenet pokollaxhno allapatserr
so'moe enkarnapa' a'porrarrenan shonte' kok po'pampo
ateth orrtena pa'tatschet pa'tatstat atma'ntat b yotnom xhen páthetets topoeñets
eso't pha'yenet acheñenesha' errothena't yenpannenet phamo'tsesha' penyo
escha' pha'yeset atthoch yonpoet berrta
attho yéxhkatenet po'shlletaph
eschá' neñot añ kellko
allempo mothenpa' épaye'ch shotare'ten yamo'tsesha' go'taso'tenet mápañkënet waso'tyenet e'ñaso'tyenet ñamha amha'tarenetpa' ñamha allempo yellarena oñpa' o'ch omarrenet toponeth allcha'ña taparerreterr ñeñthcha' alla' motherrtserr po'poñ charo
awathpa' allempó amá waxherra' poeñanesha' shonte'ch pa'namen berroxhno ñeñtho'mar yamo'tsesha'pa' amach es pallte'the
nekellka pa'socheñ kellek atthenath
rramoesh amach pellkatsto
llékëñets ñerra'm allempo' orrtena llékëñets ateth ñerra'm rroma yamo'ts o'chxho llem
yekellka patherr abchannatpan yomporépach yanantenaya o'ch nekellkonap népañer
peserrpare't atethcha' phanap
pemoecha o'chetpa' awo' oter
berroxhno nanetsro atarr shonté' eñall atesha ñamha koñetha wapo
eñé kowen noxhtat ñeth not
the'pa' perrma'nom takats petpa' pallpocha'ph ñamha po'bhath o'pono eñóteñtsopo' all pekellkën
rropotse'ñ tsách poétso'che o'ch ñamha chetampenet pa'tall
awáth allempo xhoyo'tampesye'th rreth yapa' amo'ka' arromñátheye
escha' sellkate' saphthoch ayxhatañ norrtatyes ñeth neñótwanem errpona't parant yoret ora
erra'the ye'phayes

thepa' o awenes yomporcha' sanataya
poetháporñapa' awo' och
sekwa'yes ateth phépha'nem épaph peyom
pemareta errothenthe' phayenet allempo sherbesotenet
wellesheñets
peyerrpoera ora orrtatyeñe'ts echenancha pa'socheñ ñeth eñotaten toma'ntateñe'ts yeth allcha yexhkachet yokwayerr ñeth yekellkayesnom
e'ñet kowen sephanem
eso'ch all yewomchaten
allempó pomhatséten po'ñer tso amá pokteyaye o'ch ya'pomhatsetoñ po'ñer ñeth yémethena poetsathoth ama't ñamha ontapo tharro'mar ñerra'm shá po'ñer tsapñó atserrpoeñeñenopa' o'ch pomre'tpa' ñethpa' awo'ch a'poro'yechan ñeth moetsene' berr
neserrpareñ nenanmoñcha' pamothroth pacheñer
yapxha e'pay yeyom yenanom all poktena
añeñpo xho'kmat yotyen ametheñe'ts yamotsesho
erro'then the phayenet atthó pomotenet eñe kowen
eseshathe' moechatsetenet allempo amre'tenet
pa'mother po'rroxher all wañen yeserrparen epay yeyom
ma'poch xhen anapoets
pallerr wayoll chetan koyemh tsoth anemh opono allotsen yerr pompor ñamha pachor mhorr
yethoch phontenen tsapoch pe'moenen atarr nerrothmeneñpa' amach nonteno
errpona't kañther eñall chorre' xhop
eseshakopthe kellkëñet
rráteñ át a'keshphátey
pekellka'yes koñe'thatets serrparñats so'chñetsoxhno
sokthapech ñeñth eñalletatsa ya'netsro awañaye' añcha' sa'potha' thorreñets kothaphñats ñatopa' chekmañats
kornesha' poethapor añcha' kotape'chen kowen atthoch yomporarsachet poerawo allo'tsen ñamha yochreshats
amach peserro allach pema' o'pono all moen nochkarexhno tharraña amach pemhcha'tatsto ñerra'm so'na'taph nochkar
allempoñapa' awo' wapateñeterr peph atthoch moereñerrpa' awo'xho tso'pa thematenpa' awo'xho' moerana peph awo' moerawyapa' awo'xho tharro'mar chámaspa' awepa'to rrothoñ ot
watherpa' atthoch a'matatenan tsachma' awo' poenasa acheñ watherpa' ño' yeyexhaterre' tarwasats pepenkëñotho' poenasa wather
serrparñats ma'ñorrona' awathpa' machayotho' orrterra wepoesha' yamo'tsesho nanako' kowen tsashe'mamoen pa'shtam awo' yenpare'tosan yamo'ts
errpona'n poerraremh poetsarr pechme'ten
errothena't penteñ ñeñth pe'th enoñ eso'marthe' pokte'ka' ama pokteyaye pekellka' arr eso'marthe' phanáp ateth
elena atthoch entan anapoets rroma'nman xharramoth ñamha ateth chetampesnom
thopa' tsorrmatenana pashtam
photyes ateth orrtena errponthe' émot ñamha etse'th échenet páthe'tets
allempo' yapoktateñ yeyóche pátherr cheshá ñethcha' yonañche all pathetets apxheñe'ts
esthe'ña thore'tene't attho enóñtenet
poktethé' neserrpare't añ eñóteñets epan namots tharromar
e'ñethe kowen nekellka so'chñets
phañemat ñoñets pekellkër ateth poechena'tstena taramp ato' phañemat ñoñets ñamha ñeth poechena'tstetsa
po'pocheñoñapa' awo' o'ch kok ñewa népartonaph pegor ñapa' awo'xho' anaph pepartayechpon negor xhothe' amoroxhen phontenen
yechme'ten ateth orrtena shontoche'tats
mekellpa' moénet ommanna'teñets
oth menth echene atarr yáto' yos
pe'nanom arr chetatsó esokopcha sherbeney
wayollpa' asochareth parepawoth
ommoñath allempo atthach otyenet nanako'ch sherbenet amapa' echenet
ma'ñorr époet kajore' añ moenenet kompare o'chka' yemáta
eseshathe' yéchme'taterre' pa'namen pa'paréxhno
allothpa' o'ch peñotaterrey ñeth thoratspe
nanatan koymho aspan ñamha poexhoxher papar a'nané tsó ñamha nanata'n mapoé' tso cheterran koyemh anemh allotsen yerr
sho'llet o'ka rroma ñamha phachor ñañapa' awo'xho otenerr
eso't a'methay añ kellelk
eñe noksheñesha nekellkënnaph all pethorrena tharromar o'ch newomchatenep ñamha o'ch nexhapatenaph añ kellek eñotateñets attho moeroxhtena yamots allempo pómoenet pa'namen narmets

pha'ñema't kellek ñamha phokwayer ateth allempo' yapoen kañther thekmach yeshatach mam allempopa' o'ch yaph llollo attho'ch atho'roray
aweph pha'keshpateña ma'yarr chospa' awo' máta thekma allo tsen enoñ awo'xho órrtosa poeñmañesha' enoññapa' alla poesan attho oñeñe'chenan ma'yarr
atthoch xhap chéshanesha' pa'pakllopa xhoch athma'yesnomoet apko'mhó all temantatena arrapoxhno ñeñth yapoene' yewamenk
ranto ñato' phokwe' shonteñets amnare'tets ma'poch amnar xhen yeyerpa'neñach
noxhathollpa' solltapo'cha apexho
nokthanom ateth poechenatstena kellek korreñets
moeroxhteñets
eseshathe' yomchatseten allempo yeyénpannena
ateth e'morrtena nerram allempo yeten tsach gacho
nomporpa cheshoteñ apatyeset aspanaxhno mamore'phar kakaphar
tho' ñaném wapa'moetsa pokollo
pentenat e'sot popoñetstetsa ñoñets kellke
pechta' páthe'tets kañthó ñeñth kak atthekma
allowen ñeth echene' nepa'ñerpa' atarr ásho'poth
errponthe' chópapets yexhkatenet allempo petma'ntat pa'namen chópapets ñeth pechme'ten
yañema't kellek attho shoteth awath senthephnomarnesha
mo'methollesha' shémashreshe'moe ñeth yéxhkatene' séna'teñets
e'ñech mamthoth se'mhñotyes
atethcha' yepháyes
tsathpe'ts ápexh kochell ñamha axhpoe' esthe' berroxhno yerrmáten añ shellammotho
ese'shathe' pa'cheñer
teñerochemh
ayetña arrmañ rromayeth koyanesha' parrochpa' arro' awanenet chetso all xhoñenet mampa' allo' pokteret ayetña xho'the eratame'tetpa' awo'to moetsanet ayetña allo' ontarethterret thoño apata'yesaretho pomomoro chopaphtso
e'ñet kowen petpa'nom
allempo'sañematwa esthe' moeneñ o'ch yexhatey añ kellek
pekwayer allothpa' phapoktater phañema't ñeth pekellka apotheñets allothpa' petsotsé korsapho all poktena arr chetatso
yapá yotenapañ amathe sherbeno yeñoñ ñethómar oka yepeswermo'ch yeñoñ ora anetsomar añach yeñoterr ñeth tama echar ñoñets añ xho'ch yaxha yeshoñe
o'ch yokthapech ñethcha' yeserrpare't
errponthe' nepalltena
errothenat llollo maría
tserroth ñamha yerr
esempó yétamoen ya'mropa' pokte' o'ch yemhchatse'teñ póporrona' atthoch yásotenya' eshkënoch thekma ye'nwen yetarwas ñamha amach yómxheno
eñall ora koyanesha' a yerr rroma'nman xharramoth atthoch entan anapoets
errponthe' parantake' yoret épsheño'maret
yépose'ch allowá yomneñ yerrorre' tsáchpho
eso't yexhkatyeñets phayenet koñe'th achnesha' bh phorrtatnom kellkë peyexhkat atma'ntat tsotsmet
sañyak moetsayeñ yekellkën moth kellek atarr all yamothten apoktatareth ñoñets ñamha yenen epoxh all wañen
potheshtapa' yéxhkatenan mápñek
pekwe pechkotheroth ñamha pokowenroth
attho és yeyexhkatyen allempó es yeyexhkatenpa' añcha' yeñót xhoch e'ñe kowen yakra'yes alloch es yeyexhkat ateth ñerra'm teropexh koñeshom shellapan shokosh rekërkanets ñamha pesharr allempoch yéme'chyes allempó o'yaren árrorr tharro'mar allempo' po'nna'ten atthoch nanak sherben ñeth yeyexhkatyen attheña nerra'm allempó yéme'chyes árrorrpopa' xhoch emnatenpa' mameshapa' o'ch mellasha't allothachxho' poetsowa
errawaka' thácha' pésenthe' matarñapa' awo' anáph
pha'rktampes arrapoxhno ñeth eñall pha'netsro allothpa' o'ch pétsotsa chokro ñeth eñall po'poñ anetso
eso't senten arr atma'ntatareth
yapxherra attho'ch yokwamperr pa'namen arrapoxhno pokte' o'ch yeshonte'rra yanetsro errach yexhkachet
esthe' yeperr atthoch yekwamper ya'netser
sa'ñema't añ akellkareth allothpa' señotatey esthe yexhateney tharraña atthoch setsepa' pa'namen poetsathllomh añcha' yeñot poeñoteñ yatañneshañ attho ñetpa' tsepateteth poetsathllom
thepa' o'ch petpat ayerpoxhen ñeth yexhateneph ayxhatañ nésochena
o'ch yeyerpaterrsa apanesha thepa' xho'ch yenare't mam all yeporra pamro eñoteñtsopawo' ayxhatañ sa'ñematerr epas se'yem
pemñot eñe moecheth atthoch peyxhe ñeth oten
séye ñoñets ñeth sentwa serrpare'teñtso
esokopthe' sherben añ epe' parteneythe añ apexh
péserrpare't párro peyemnésha' phoch peyemnésha' escha' perret alloth
patherr berr ñeth yetañene yamromar
sanrremh
e'moeñeto'ch rrana'nena attheñapa' awoch moma'wanerra pa'pakllo atthekmo'ch pena erra órrpa' atthochxho o'waño esesha' wa'ñe ama't orrwanenentpa' amo'ch wa'ñeñeto ama't atethpa' ñothochxho' wapá allempoñpa' amoch esesha' moeñoterraye
attho poesheñarr enoñ e'nenan shometeñets
námetheñ nénoñeta all wañen époxh
parrochña poesheñarr yamotspa' awo' awenerr poetsatho o'ch e'neneta' shepan ñethcha' rra'nenet xhepa'toch paya'teñechyesa amo' eñóterro alloth on
allempo yémhten ñerra'm errá yésen
yexhateñets yakren pa'namen yepoer phokwa' a'ma'ntatareth allothpa' o'ch yeserrpare't
womenke'shatamhphseñets
all yexhayena berroxhno
xhachka' kompare nemeshaphña añetholleshaka' petkathollesha' epa't
añpa' othetholl nanak atsrre'mñath nanakcha' kothare'tenan tse'm bero'te
thempo yexhena oñsasomar
esempó ya'bellenpa' e'ñech mamthotha ñamha yoksheñesha'ch yépeñ atthoch ama atsrre'mare'teto o'ch sekellka' ma'pa a'poktañoñtatareth atheth a'belleñet
kothapecheñ errothencha' akrratan pakñether tharromar xha atsnaten
eso'marthe'escha' eñótatey añ kellek
allempo tso'poen apapa' xhoch moéchatse'tenan mom
allothpa' o'ch allá' phañema'tererr eñe mamthoth
omarra po'noñthet
llechap ñeth chorrena ablleshe'mañ abell ñeth ablleñshe'm
the'pa' o'ch werawesh ño'ñá enterraya' awo' wapater korneshesho' sha'rephñapa' awo' otan kornesha' the'pa' peyexhkatat amnar shetamoets alloch nerrmoer yompor eshkënoch amach xhá a'potawano pa'tsrroña
rrarets ñeth pén ach
eseshathe' enamoenet llesens
escha' sellkatyese' saphthoch ayxhatañ yokwampen all yexha'yena berroxhno yexheñets yeserrpare't
eso'cha yexhatan atma'ntatareth
eso't chetanen wakësh ñamha esokopthe' sherben
errponthe' kellé agapoet
attho yénatenet pátherr rrenarotats ñethcha' choyo'mhtet atarr kowen amhcha'tareth po'rrnarot
o'ch pekellka' chétatso pa'socheñ pochkar kanawasath ñeñth eñall pha'netsro
tharro'mar esempó yekellkërrer po'pocheñopa' o'ch ya'paxharrtenerr yékllek
topomarneshapá awo'ch awanmoet poetsatho xho'ch waxhataterre't berroxhno ateth ñerra'm
eso'mare't ápoeñet po'nmenesha' ñeñth nanom yexhkaten shepshesha
apa' kankënan posholl ñeth ena' po'chopapho
attho yéthore'tena allempo yeparetyena amách yekellkëna o'ch yañema't morreñets
eso'marthe' séchena ach poetsatho
ote'n thó xho'ch pethoreta ñamha o'ch pechmetyes epexhnó kenkewash attho'ch perrmá kakaxhno
koñeshom pesharr moerrell ponllomh theyoshke' peñót errotchencha' pétsetanom ormetsoxhno
apoktachet eseshach rrachet ñeth wañenet
yañema't kellkó ateth nare'tenet mam topo moth a'ñemateñets
eñallcha' apkometh
eso'marthe' kowenan llollo árrorr
yexhateñets yeserrpare't attho yokwa'yen all po'nyen arraepoxhno
arankmatholl allempoña atsnerrpa' oxho' alla a'terr a'terr aterr a'noserra pa'pakllo
ya'ñema'ten atthoch yekellkën attho yenamoeñ llesens allempo yokshame'tena
serrparñatsoth orrtateñe'tsthe morreñetsthe ñewa photerr eso'marthe' poktethe' o'ch yemorrecha' morreñets
peserrpare't epaph peyem ñeth serrparñats sañematwaallothpa' sokthapech añ pa'namen a'phthoteñsoth
yérra'yen ñamha yókya'yen yenarmexhno yañema't serrparñats ñamha yeñora
peyo'chayes e'paph peyom ñeth atthekma setmantat
o'ch serrparete't epoet poe yem allempo o'ch anapoet ñeñtha apthotanet ayxhatañ ñethcha' yeyenpoe' ayxhatañ erra't yeyexhkateñ yexhateñtsopawo
atsótenana poñ tharraña apartañpa' o' áph pátherr bereth atarret pátherr bereth atarret añ nashanor xho atsna'ten añ nashanor xho atsna'ten
yañematerrerr akellkarethallempo yanap aphthoteñets
oten newomchena parayos phakrraterren nachporrena ama nerró' a'ch arrorr
pekellka ora ñeth petsotwanem
allempo' yexho'ñen mampa' xho'ch ápateney po'chets
yekellkën ñeth kowen yent all atma'ntatarethó ñeth yokwanene o'ch wañerranerr o'ch yanap a'phtho'teñets
yeserrpare't attho sherbesoten yanesha
o'ch ot ñeñth tomantena serparrñats ñeñth em errothenchaña ta errothench wañ ñethcha' yeyenpoe' ayxhatañ ñamha ach
eso't nanak pha'yen cheshanésha' all atma'ntataretho eso't rrema'yenet eso't ñanem pét
esthe' penet nerra'm ama xhoñeneta' mam
sowapat rekërkanets ñamha arrcha sewapa' pokollo atarrpawo' setsotsé x ñeth yeso'chen ñapoéth
penamh phamotsesha ñamha tho' ñeth atarr anare'tañ peyo'cha pátherr serrparñats ñeth serrpare'tatas tho' allothpa' seserrpareterr
xhoch yápoeñ poesheñarr po'nmenesha ñeth ñanom yeyexhkaten atthoch yeñwenach ñerra'm ñá amá pokteyaye o'ch yerramampes poesheñarr kañthro esempo ama es yeyoreno xhoch yerramoen kañther
ateth ñerra'm atthó yaññoten yenaremhpá añchá ñanom yephanem
atthoch eñótañtetpa' año'ch kothape'chatenawet po'nmeneshare' ñamha esempópa' awoch orret pa'par ñeñth cheme'tenet
yetpoen pa'llpochaph chekmats topamtso ñeth yechme'ten ya'poktateñ o'ch yesherbeso't yexheñets yeserrpare't
kowenat yemñotyes ñeth eñorathsa
eso't exho'manatenet
yañemat ñamha yéye atthekma all kowentena akellkareth allempó po'nen yenaremh xho'ch
sewashpa' yexhatenan poechemer yaneshaxh
photwer apa' ñamha ach o'ch serrpare'tataph ateth poerraremh ñeth rrayen berroxhno ñamha othexhno
añ cheme'tateñtso pokte amá nekellkëthe pa'socheñ nekellkëthe ateth orrtena

chech ñeth xhorene' wena weñets tsachmoro cheratstena wello
errpona't poe'mer échen xhopoech
errothenat yeparteyena
yentateñ berroxhno
errothencha yéso'ch
attho rromoen paherr béth
se'ye ñoñets ñeth sentwa serrpare'teñtso
allempo abellenetpa' xho yenpannenet koyaneshare asheñorrare eñe pokte' nenteñ eñe pokte' ñeth phayen koyaneshare allempo akoshenet xhoñenet mamtapecheñet a'poteñet ñamha aptsarrteñet
añ eñota'teñe'ts ñeth notyes kowenthe' neño'chthe' ñeth otyes neyem
yeserrpare't esthe' yekellkayes
topanets ñamha pa'yathpa' año' yexhkateñet therrothpano
yexheñets yeserrpare't épay yeyom
koshame'tamets shonte' yatañnesha' ma'yochenet ñamha parasyoso'teñet yompor yato' parets attho ápanet bensampeñets
sentat sekellkëñoth patherr atma'ntatareth
allñapa' yonna'tampsosa xhepa'tcha' poetallsa noñth
kasha'ñapa' awo otan shopshesha' arr naneneph nemapoetaño allempo shepsheshapa' awo kowan kasha' nanako' rremosheñ añña shepsheshapa' awo ot poeyoxhro
tharromar nanak moeroxhteth acheñenesha pachporrñoth
phanap aphtoteñets pekellkarrmo yexhateñets ñethcha' yetsot eseshat orrtate ñeth yetsoten
yanap añ a'phtho'teñets
añmapa' pátherr topash
eso'cha' kellek yekellka' eso'mare'cha yekellkë' peyexhkat alloch pémña pékllek
ma'pa yakren pa'namen yopoer yexheñets yeserrpare't
pañthoma'th kellmeshepo'reren yexhena oño'mar

che'w
awathpa' eñallo patherr acheñ apnasañ ñapa echane'thó poechemer amo árrorrño allo'ch anen paxhnopho
napaxho' not ateth nokthape'chen
pa'nemen pa'tall ñamha yérareshe'm ñeth amá sherbetso
errpona'cha' kak anerret páthe'tets atthekma
ye'mhñoten ateth sherbeso'tete'th awath sañema't ñamha se'kellka' se'kwa' atma'ntatareth allothpa' o'ch yeserrpare't
thépa' pekellka' koñeth kellek ateth orrtena pather berr ñeth kowen penteñ ñamha pena'yes epoxh all poktena
eso't senten arr a'tmantataretho
allempotheñ eñotere't ateth ñerra'm
erra'the kellko yenayeñ aphthoteñets
allempoñapa' awo't noch ayxhatañ awo't ellerrenpa' xhaptsayepa'cha athasatho
attheñapa' awo' morrencha awo' yexhach attho es yerrmoen a'rrothrexha'toñ poegor atthoch chetampes poemoshnañ allempótheñpa' ñeñth yamotspa' ñerra'm sen go'atspa xhokmo'ch rremoenan pa'namen ñeth moenen alloch shotatenan pakñethar ñamha pamo'tsesha' nésochena
errotenat yakren alloch yeyexhkaten shotamets
apá' atsne xho kothapecheñ errothencha' akrratan pakñether tharromar xha atsnaten
epo'tsen atarr poenan shonte' pa's matena pa'pa'yó tsama'th pa'smell
yethñats allpon llollopa' o womhcherra
wena'tampenan tse'm poeberror
sapa' sekellkëthe' etserra'serrparñats
yoten allempo yetsorrpoellecheñ oth ama atollop
yeposwawerepach pa'parexhno
yexhateñets shomemhtamets alló amá ya'kllateno berroxhno phokwa' atma'ntátareth allothpa' o'ch yeserrpare't
yewapaterpa' xhoch ye'rrama'wer nanak sherben o'ch yeñóch allempó yechcha'teñ kañther mampa' o'ch yexhapaterpa' xhoyach yo'pawerre' allempoñapa' o'ch moentasapa' o'chxho ye'rramawer atthoch ameswerr ñamha llollo

porets póretspa' año' yeyexhkateñ komonápano
errothenat penan potasher
awath allempo ponpenetpá xhoch wañeñet pamotsesha añekop yenpanateteth atthoch enwenet mamesha ñethchá thorret potarwas
páthe'tets cheshanesha' rrancha' no'cho
yexhateñets shomemhtamets alló amá ya'kllateno berroxhno pkokwa' atma'ntatareth allothpa' o'ch yéserrpare't
amach yekellko shonte' h ñoñtso pelleye' añ okpa' wapatyenet ñeñth yexhkatatenet pa'nyo ñamha etserratatyenet pa'namen ateth ñerram
yorrtat kellkëts pa'tatsmeto ñamha yeyexhkat atma'tat tsotsmet
ye'na óñ koymho o'ch yéshat mapoe' atsérr allempo' o'ch ye'kamáta kashemtso
kowen yenteñ ñerra'm yeyenpannena
pha'ñema't añ kellek amach pha'ñemateña' o'ch phanap añ a'phtho'teñets
poktethé' penten ateth oten koyaneshatholl
yemchatse'teñ wather thopa' oten
añ yeñoñ ñeth apoeyña yato' parets allochña

otteñe'chareth

año'ch werro

ashothpe'll
thepa' o'ch señorayesa ateth e'morrtena pathetets kellek
ama'ch yeyamatsto ontapo ñeth ñerra'm wasotetpa' xho'ch shatnerre't oñ all wasotet atthoch kowen orrerrerrá' kakathollesha
yeyellsheñe'ch yonsame'teñets ñethcha' kotha'nem ayxhatañ ayxhatañpa' o'ch yellsheñe'ch pampo
poktethe' o'ch yetantater poephar thó o'ch yekellkayes
a'mñetstareth
yokthapech pathetets serrparñats ñeth yemyes ñamha yañema'tyes ñethcha' yekellka arr
anets pa'socheñ ñeth enene arrápo poetsatho
petsotse póktapho ñeñth phokthapechen ateth serrparñats
o'ch nañemat serrparñats allothpa' petso'tse ñeth poktetsa
pekellka pokta toñeth kellweñoñets alloth o'ch pekwé ñamha phanap
yanesha attho yécherr epe' atthó enoñtena yanesha'pa' xhoka'ye poerráterran poephar poramasa
wa'ñeñets xhoyotampesya sherbe'so'teñets moechatse'teñets
pha'ñemat pekllek peyemakop
awo' meten amnar tomash atthoch tarwaseneta' awo' kothan po'poñ yamots po'nanesha' atthoch yenpa'yes all potarwaso
errponacha' shomall agapyeset páthe'tets
esokëpthe' sherbenen o'ch seyenpoeñe't sáto' peotyes peyem pechmetenat popon apartañ ñeñth eñotyene esokmañen
errosheña't errosheña't penonesha' atsóshe'moe' po'kashe'm
rañthana tsa'ta poechá anapoets
nathope'per chepha chepharenet allempó choporrenet allempó senathetarenet
attho shecho'teñet cheshatholl
thépa' pekellkë xharra so'chñets aso'chañ koñethó xharra so'chñets aso'chañ atarroth

peñets ñeñthcha' eñalletatsa ñeñth enoñpa' atsna't
atthe't pépha'nem phamha

rro'tstamhpeñets

yekellka kowen paxharr yorrtát

oth ñeth achpa' xharenan okllarrém po'kashe'mo

a'parrpe'ch atsrretho atthoch po'rrarrpe'ch
arro'noth
yeñema't ñeth echén añ serrpare'teñets ñethcha' yentát
atthach otatsetyen pamotsokop
añ ñoñetspa' echenan e'pa poyoxher ñeth akowentene' phañema't pa'namen ñoñets paxharr pe'yanem
kowenat orrta añ kellëk
newomchach neyom ñamha norrtat ñeth neñoten
errpona't acheñenesha' amá rañthaye yexhkatyeñets
pamtharr tsaka'mpa' awo' ontanna'tet époet yell allempó o'yarerr yellpa' oten
yapoktatnomh yeyá aphkomethó atethchá yekellkanom atthenath
yetma'ntatyes ñamha yorrtatyes atma'ntat tsotsmet ñamha tsotsmet apko'met
errpona't patapets palltena o'ch ne'nwa netarwas
pompor tserro'th yoran kañther toñerochemh
tharraña amo' eseshaye' eñótaye'thé attho' ñapá cheme'tenan pa'par atsnañets ñeth so'chetsa cancer
esthé otnom wather eso'marthe rranampes pasomoe
sotyes ñeth atarr kowen sent serrparñatso
phañema't kellek ñeth pentwanom allothpá pekellka atthemath apoktatareth ñoñets
nanakcha' tsa'ma'tena
esokopthe' kellkët añ serrparñats
eso't yexhkatyeñets yomena cheshanesha' eso't yexhkatyeñets amá yomeneto
phañema't ñeth oten thó ñamha llollo allothpá pekellka ñeth phokthapech
sho'llet atthach pemorren allempoñapa' xhepa'toch ómachme'ta awo' yaware'ta xhepa'toch palltame'ta awo' to'reshoñet all yawena attho' koweñet all penká womenk sho'llet arrnoma awo' ot
tsama'th pa'shtamatholl ñerra'm epotaypa' ama't allponmat ya'phller o'ch alla atserrterrra
eso't narmetsoxhno nare'tet
womhchan o'ch awey porrayo all póserr oñ nasecheñ chetsorrpa' xho kéllen amá secheno ko'chñapa' chetsorr parrokmach yorrena oñ póserrsasen awo'xho awanmoet párro chopechetsetopa' machayotho' oñchet poesheñar enoñ allo' oñeñechenan atotholl kochñapa' awo' otan chetsorr
allempo che'tenet xhach ojojatstena' koyaneshare' a'yotheñ e'morrtena all ojojatstena ne'yey
phokwa' añ ametheñe'ts ñamha phañemach ñeth kellkëtsa
yexhateñets yekwamhpen all ye'nen shota'poets ye'nyen all yáshóta'yen
allempó yesherbesotenpá eñech awathekma yema'nena atthoch yorramoen yeshorror pamtharrmeñcha' o'ch allempoña o'ch poetareswenpa' o'ch nampset shelletapho awo' kornesha' o'ch chete poetarr pajópa' o'chxho athoré yató partséshakop tharromarcha' kowenet atsné ñethpá pochoyomh yompor
sa'ñema't ñeth sekellka allowen seyóm ñamha seserrparetách samots
eñé ñoksheñoth masheñ ñemneñ esempo'ch phañemat añ kellëkpa' womchapcha' ñethomar yomneñ o'ch pemo'tenya tharromar phapa penter phañema't kellëk allothpa' phanap a'phtho'teñets ateth oten kellëk
yekellkën tema'nteñe'ts attho' yatsepen pa'namen pa'parexhno
ma'ñorr ñamha posho'll parroch ma'yarrpa' xho' moen patsoth tsach poellakto posho'llñapa' e'ño eno tsachmo'ro
o'ponoth sótatsopanach
senayes pa'socheñ eño'teñets kellek atma'ntataretho
oñsas ñeth wetsa achamachepnoth
allempo yethomoena amapa' ethomoeney warexhno'teñets
napa' nayatena atollop chancho esha ñamha wakësh
allempo wapotamhphsateñets
rreth awathpa' eñallo' allempó xhoyo'te'th rreth ñapa' nanako' a'mñeñath
eko'reñets
sanáp a'phthoteñets allothpa' sa'ñemat serrparñats shornañets
yeserrparen ateth amethayen othexho' pa'namen othexhnopa' a'metheney atthoch e'ñe marepa' ametheney atthoch amá yechokro allempo koshenapa' e'ñech kowen tonaya allempo llekënapa' o'ch es yepasoya ñetho'mar allempopa' eñech yeñótnoma
yeyerpoera ñeth serrpare'tatey tho' allothpa' petmantat tome' xho'pmo' phaptho'tyes phamots erróthena't yenpannenet allempo tarwasenet pamro
añ wakeshapa' áxhomen
pewapa amách pepsere awo'en petsotsé x all poktena
attheña ñerra'm poechenarrowa yénare'chpa' esempó yamre'terrerrpa' o'ch eñalletyesa nethcha' yepatare'tepa' amachxho yenare'two
peserrpare'tach ayxhatañ añ kellëk ateth yokthapechnom ñanom
thepa' pekellka ñeth eñotatay pa'cheñer kellek ñamha errothenthe wañen allothpa' pegach peyom
pekellka' othexhno pa'socheñ ñeñth pechme'ten
yorrtat paso'cheñ ñethcha' yeserrpare'tat
otteñe'cheñets añ yoten ñeth otteñe'chen o'ch anmet carcelo amapa' tompoet ñeth pánten
parantpan kochlletholl tsachpethollesha' phokwayes atma'ntatareth allothpa o'ch pechta' papllethollesha' allotsen parant poe'nor
all yamothten kellkats
noxhpa' metanenen méteñets
eñotentsopo' waksho' yeth
yétansa ñeth yemorrechena
allempo méllashañet yoshak yeshta'm o'ch martset
pa'namenakopña sherben kamello
popotantañpa' xho'ch ro'pechenet eñe kowen
popoñonethpa' ñeñth ñeñth agëne ñoñets
allempo anen poepo'taropa' ñerra'm échenan paknorpa' ñach kothape'chatene' erróthencha' korrena esempoch sométa erróthencha' kothape'chaterran ñamha pakñéthar erróthencha' e'ñe kowen korra époet poerrollar ñamha pamo'tsesha' atthoch ayemañéthtena ñamha amach atsrre'mñathteno eñech kowen alleshonkaten
thépa' o'ch ya'ñema't atthó thórrayena anets ashañenkanesha
pékellka'yes chetatso poérets ñeñth péchme'ten pha'netsró pétma'ntat poérets ñeñth eñall pha'netsro pekellkarrmo
ayxhatañpa' o'ch xhore'tan cheshanesha' o'ch yellsheñe'chet ñewa ateth yeyenpoen yepakllo ateth ñerra'm koyaneshathollpa' o'ch tepátatan ateth yeyoren yokrramh attheña asheñorrarepa' o'ch tema'ntet ateth ñerra'm xho e'nenet kak eneta' tsella'theph rrarenet tsach a'matenet tsach poretaso'tenet atethcha' yellsheñe'chyeset o'ch ya'phthotanet kowenthe' o'ch yeyenpa' ñethcha' yeyenpoe' ayxhatañ erra't yeyexhkateñ yexhateñtsopawo
pekwe' ateth poen apoktañoñtatareth yaneshaxh
esempopa' awo'ch otwerr añe yethropa' amá nentó pe'tok nanak rrape' o'ch allokchamechetpa' ñañapa' alloch rromoenan po'tasher pasmell atthoch amá e'potamphseto
peyenpanet e'nwe' páthe'tets
petpa'nom pa'tarrer épa'tets chekmats perrma'nom tsotsamet
allowen ñeth rro'notets
amá cheme'teneto kelle' ch
pampa'weñeta'pa' awo'xho'ña awanerret pokollo
e'ñe ñotha tanterra amá tantaterran
peyexhkát ápotmhot allothpa' o'ch péserrpare'tach ayxhtañ esokëpthe' yemo'teñ apartañ ñamha esthe' nanak échen alló thorrena parteñtsopawo
ye'nayes ñethcha' kowe' ñeth eso'ch yepha' errothenach yapxha
a'shontareth
yeyenpannena atthó yeponpen yenaremh
atthey napa atarren óten neshamllorr añethólla neklle añethóllesha ñerra'm xho' nomoñeten napa atéth nan nompor ñató añthe nagapa na'to' ateth yepena ñanom ama yesena poetsathó ñanomcha o'ch yeyoranom epe' mañorrokop o'ch yamotanem o'ch awey ñerra'm yatoros koshthe amach yesanacheñe'thekop ama yamtache ñerra'm yamté atthach yephá yerreña ñanompa xho'ch yethóreta
peyasoch allpon o'machet poesheña'tets allothpa' o'ch pékelka' e'ñot allpon poktena pa'tatstát wallatatenopa' o'ch petmantáta ñamha allpon mápoe' pha'nosa
esthe thoreteñets etsotnomoet pathetets
teñeroch shekmech therro'tech pa'pakëll pepe a phokwa' alleneth kowa'yen tsáchpe'ts allcha' phonañcha'nma
serrparetateney thó' atho yechechen allempo yechten yexhkateñets xhoch yéche'chnen allempó ye'nen alló es yeyexhkaten
moth añemateñets yañema't pa'socheñ yanapoen a'phtho'teñets
pekwa'nom phokthape'ch pentnom ñeñth kothets
eso'chaña yeñót atthoch yeyexhkat allo'ch yerrma kak
tsapathamoena ach otenen yerr mama
awo' sanamochan koshthepa' awo'xho epote' pona pa'tko nanakëpa'toch atsotana po'ponas xho' rranaretach attho' ot
yemhchatseteñ oño'marnesha' attho yasho'ten oñothpa' añ poktetsa o'ch yemhchatseten pamo'mte' oño'mar ateth ñerra'm
allempoñapa' awo' otanet pachor
allempo tarwasateñetpa' ama't ama rráteñeto ñamha ama onáteñeto oñ pa'tatsmatpa' amach rromo
allempoñapa' awo'xho' alla poenasa
awepa'to' apnase'twanet ayots
abe'tatsñath
yoten ateth
peya'nom tsotse' chopeph peyocha'nem allpón choph ena'moen páthe'tets
arrcha' phanorros enka
oten llollo ñewa pewapat pe'mar
o'ch yañemat o'ch chétatey o'ch morre'chatey kowena't penten morreñets
abetheñets
amorreñath arepene'thcha' she'rarats yethoch moen xhoxh xhaxharexhaten allcha' tappoen poechoyor
cheta'yeñe't ñowapoth atthoch mekell xhap koshapampó entyesosan pánamen nentare
añ kellek chemetateñets echenan noñets all orrtenena ñeth pen sochñets añ sochena peñets
pe'nwa ñeth palltetsa
eso't rrarets koñe'th tsa'tetsa
parrochñapa' awo ot kornesha' atthoch moererrya yompor xhoch yekwer épsheña cheshathollesha' ñeñth ama ochña'tetsa' poesheñarr asheñorr awo' ota'moenan po'xh
errat eñall pa'parexhno
machayotha wapa patherr cho'sotholl awo'ch aphlleññaña' pa'shop oshkollethollñapa' omacha xha't poesnomh o'ch kowerrpa' a'yentha omacha allñapa' totphasotosa poellakto xhepa'cha' rorta rór rór allempotheñ amá ottaterro ñerra'mathe' xho moen pátherr oshkolletholl
allempo o'metame'tena po'chets poerexh poe'mokro
thepa' o'ch sañemach mamthoth ñethcha' yeñot athoch yeshomenta oñoth ñerra'm semneñ o'ch senoñta oñothpa' añcha' setsotnom
errpona't chópeph kotha'nom kowenoth
esesha'ch kompare a'nosaya pechap aspenethpa' ñeñthcha' poñellatats yompor nemñe' atthoch amach sese'chareno kornanesha' poetháporpa' awo ot
errothencha' neyaphchaso't ñoñets
peserrpare'tatey poxhopoñ phamo'ts allothpa' petma'ntach
rrartsorexh
amách yetho'tena yókrramh o'ch yomchatsetnom yompor paréts attho'ch atontatonay yenaremh
petma'ntat ñeth yañema'twa kellko' petsotsé korsapho pa'namen peserrpare'terr ñamha pekellka ñeth peñotyes añ serrparñatso
errpona't yom eñall koshtallethollo
allempoñapa' awo' otapoer pamnarmatñoch sonterrna' allothñapa' awo'xho' onaxherret pa'paklleto
a'mhter esho'ter
thothma'ttoma'ch atsrretho atthoch pórrarra' calentar agarexha'ch
añeñpo waxherra shonte poeñanesha' ch
poktet añ kellek añematareth
mañellaepoet poeñaresha pamtharr yethpa' awanmoet popoer ñethcha' nare'tet pamro otanet allempo' yénare'ten attho'ch kowencha' chepyen ñamha me'taren
xhoch yápoeñ poesheñarr po'nmenesha ñeth ñanom yerrmoen
neyem rosapa' axhomen
errponthe' asheñorrare' ñamha koyaneshare' tarwasets
eñóteñe'ts yesherbeso'teñ párets eso't senten arr atma'ntataretho
xharro amhaten tsetse chekarmecho
allempó yesen poetsathopa' akophach es yemoñe'tnena allochñapa' enech yonteñ o' mata berr ateth ñerra'm ro'këph rroth amapa' arrothe'tañ chemerrña ñerra'm yéxhapmoch pa'thephopa' o'ch yáthomos mame' ñato' esempopa' eñech mameshapa' o'chxho' matosa esempopa' o'chxho yematat apha ñerra'm akopha yesenpa' e'ñech yonteñpa' o'chxho yesane
xhen xharra'tets ñeñtho'mar xháp anapoets eñóteñtsopawo all yekellkën eñall asheñorr ñamha koyanesha' errponthe' cheshanesha' eñall ora
eso'cha' yeñót ñamha escha' yepha allempo a'bellenet
attho'ch a'matet tsách ñanompa' xho'ch a'tsepet tsáchphar allothpa' allempoñapa' ñerra'm tharro'mar a'ptho'teñets
errothenthé morrecheth yamots allempo ponpenet
pemñotanet allempo peserrparetatanet ñeth peñot eñoteñtsopawo
xho'ch atsepet ateth thore'tenet
allempo yekellkën pa'so'cheñ anets atesha ñerra'm
tsapathekmach pegáten epéxhno the'pa' neñóch nanakëpa't sherbeney epéxhono
oten awathpa' eñallo patherr acheñ ñeth sochetsa achallo ñapa' ña kowampene ora kakaxhno añthe yot añ kakaxhno pompor
esokpa't sherbeney páthe'tets yexhkatyeñets
yekellkën ñeth pokte sent añ kothapñats attho yeyexhkatyen pa'namenare yeñoteñ ñeth sherbets
poktet penteñ ateth pha pasomoe
añekop ora cheshaneshakop pha'netsro
e'ñotenan ach ma'pllomha chech
allempo ñeth o'ponotsenpa' o'ch awo' a'yoth
llecháp ósmamoen moene' wallama'th
nechen nás tharraña amá naxheno échethen tharraña amá neshorreno
o'ch na'torpe'ch jerekonañ o'ch nemote allempopa' o'ch alla nepoerrerra
poerrarem xhop ñamha mam
charem arr yenteñ pokollo yamro tsácho esthe' yanen yamro attho'ch yenaret yenaremh
erratsena'tña poe'ñrroña kak atthoch yetorke meshet
ametheñe'ts ametheñe'ts ametheñe'ts eso'marthe petso'tse thépa' pekellkë phanap a'phtho'teñets paxharr
eñótoxhta'teñets erro'thenat es orrtaten
atthoch ama yemxherro añcha' yemhchatse'teñ póporrona' añ kellek ñeñthcha' pha'ñematpa' añ abhcheñets ñeñth kellkën poesheñarr ayxhatañ ñeñth yexhatene' pa'tats xheñets añekop etsoterr yanesha' pha'ñemat ñoñtsoxhno allothpa' pena'nom pokte' ñamha ama pokteyaye all poktena
yerr a phanap a'ptho'teñets
atthothapa' awo'xho'ña tsepampsan shekëmh poeñrroñaña shekëmhpa' xhepa'toch rrata'nerranña ommoñathetall shekméchoth awo'xho'ña e'tpetsa'wer shekmechemh patso
so'chñets awathnaneshañ ancestral yanesha' apasñath
sosey ñeth nanak apoxhen sosyaren
eso't perr yamo'tsesha' sherenkmaso erra't awanmoet ñét och eneñeta
yapoktatyes yapxha mapsheñatets yañema't añ esthé' socha' añ kellek yexhateñets
yapxherra attho'ch yokwamperr pa'namen arrapoxhno pokte' o'ch yeshonte'rra yanetsro allcha yephayes
po'sñetollñapa' xhepa'toch rrananma ñerram poenasmarenpa' awo'xho' rranareterranet
añ épsheña asheñorrpa' échete'tho' poechamoelleñ all sechen pachor
xhoch es atsótena
ya'ñema't yokthape'ch ñamha yekellkë' pepe yexhkatenan rekërkanets pe'ñotnom allpón topoena páthe'tets
yáp yexhena poetsatho chopechen tsapo rrenan
péye' ñamha petma'ntat ñeth kothets alloth
phapoktat peserrpaña pekellkarmo pokwanem añ chetats
pepe kellka'nenan yeth allempoch nare'tatse'tet chetso
thónesha apanesha' oteñet poechemeresha' ateth
petsotse all poktena añ akellkareth
petmantat ateth pekellka ñeth thorrapotets
poktethe' penteñ o'ch penare't añ arrapo
ro'kperrém
mhorr époet yerr tsa'tet kellé épsheño'maret
eso'marthe' pátherr chésha kothenan tho' poetsathó seyerpoera ñeth sentnom atma'ntataretho allempo o'ch setmantatach samha arr ñeth sechmeten
erra'tsena't échenet pha'netsro
yenyopa' eñall shonte' pa'namen arrápo' ateth ñerram mam parant petoka ñamha pa'namen atsompapo' ñeñthpa'xho' nanak yomeña pa'namen kakaxhno
phapa' arepa't phapthá petarwaseno ñeñtho'marepa't pe'nwapna'ten chets
poerrarmexhnó atsompápo' poerraremh atsompápopa' añ sochenet pa'namen ñeñth me'tyets poetsátho'mar
allothñapa' e'ño awathekma wenapa' atthó pasa'wena e'ño' xhetsa pa'pakllopa' awo'xho' a'tsatstewena e'ño' mameshpa' awo'xho' pa'nathtá awo' thaya a'methaweñ amach nokrro tharro'mar añ nentoñ ma'ñorr pamo'mte' ñeñth otenét to'ra'm
errpona't tsella'theph shonta' ranto
eso'mare't kellkët añ kellek
eñóteñe'ts yesherbeso'teñ párets sanap pa'namen a'phtho'teñets
yoten allempo axhomentena koyanesha
allempo' yapoktateñ yeyóche pátherr chesha' ñethcha' yonanche all pathetets apxheñe'ts
ya'ñematen tema'nteñe'ts attho' partatsetenet pa'parexhno
shemake shemake tome shemake chomh shemake xho' kañther cho'ch tome cho'ch shemake chomh petmántat neth phokshate' pekellka ñoñtsoxhno all poktena
yekellka serrpare'teñets attho'ch yeñoterr shoteñets
achankëllpa' añetholla xhokmo'ch morrechena
moth añemateñets nemneñ neñot nañemat ñeth neño't nañematwa phañema't kellek phapoeth mamthoth allothpa' pekellka esthe' oten
errponthe' momáph yoret épsheño'maret
attho'ch yapoktat esomarchá' yabella
errothenat phañema'tererr añ kellëk phanap aphthoteñets
pokte't senteñ ñeñth pha'yen yátañnesha' escha' yéperr atthoch amach wañerro ñeñth yarro'tampenaya
eso'maret nanak pemtsanatennan nayara kaspareñpa' awo'xho anaph
eñé ñoksheñoth ñewomcha'tenep masheñ nemneñ esempo'ch phañema't añ kellëkpa' womchapcha' napa' añekop nekellkën o'ch ñeñotateneph yapa añe semanaro o'ch yorrtat poeñoteñ yatañneshañ ateth sherbeso'teteth awath
añeñpopa' pokte'the' o'ch yépóre'tasotyes
poktethe senten o'ch yecher pats allcha yamrerr berroxhno
eseshathe' pa'cheñer ñeth ñeth sochena añ ñ th eñotateñets'nanak kowen nenteñ poktenathe o'ch yañemach atthoch yeñot esthe eso'marcha' ya'ñema't añ eñotateñets
pha'ñema't mamthoth añ kellek allothpa' peserrpare't
thepa' o'ch alla phañematerrerr akellkareth allothpa' o'ch esesha't pa'cheñer añ a'metheñets
pénayes ñoñets all pellayena yamots akellkaretho' allempó ñanom yeyexhkatarpa yáph pátherr attho'ch bensampsarech
pha'netsropa' eñalle't ñeñth eñótene' xhópoñats
errothencha yephanom attho'ch yakowenet sekellek
allempoña ñetpa' attho' yeterret alloth ama't amá thore'twenetapa' awo' alla eñórana'tannerret attheña awath ñerra'm xho thoretet allempo rromatenetpa' esempowach xhoretwet
pekellka' eso'marthe' poktena o'ch yenare'terr pareshe'mats
errponthe' chomoer anapoets
eñóteñets ya'mre'ten allcha' yénare't xhop seserrpare't ateth senten atma'ntataretho
sanáp pa'namen a'phtho'teñets
ror awo' yexhkatan sa'p allcha ayatana kak topoena m allpochap m bhath
errothena'cha' pentnom anapoets
thathall rrenan meshet
po'tasher no'tasher patarashka
llecheñ ñerra'm poesheñarra' llechene' tsach tso' atthoch korra
errathe' anets orrtena añ atma'ntatareth
sochñets shonte' ranto josé tserro'th a errpona't kak a'kowentet ma'psheño'maret
esthe' yenpoen asheñorrothollesha' ateth tarwasen apá pa'mropa' épaye'ch thorrena atthoch es po'nets erróthena't peyenpoeñ phamo'mte' allempó amre'tenet
pétsotse péyochach ñeth pa'par a'methen
atethcha
yénareterrepach páreshemaxhno páreshemaxhnopa' nanak sherbeney ateth ñerra'm epéxhno keñkeweshexhno ñeñth anare'tareth ñamha poetsatho'mar tharro'mar allo párte'th yátañneshañ attho womhchete'th áton ñamha allo eñótañtete'th ñamha enoñtete'th
pekellka' popoñ ñoñets ñeñth yeñotatene' errathe' és petsa
errpon'cha kellé tsa'ta martha
pekwa'yes atma'ntátareth erra't yexhena añ berroxhno ñamha kakaxhno
pe'nanom arr chetatsó ñeth palltayena
awo't penter
pho'ch peyom o'ch añematonap pekllek
thoratsteñets

ateth chemnaterra awath ñeth pa'llerr lleseñ palltasareñ awathpa' eñallo' poesheñarr pa'llerr po'nmenesha' ñetho' sochatse'th palltasareñ ñapa' arro' yexhe'th ñapoeth kompreshmaño po'ñeso moenaserma'tho' allempopa' eñallo' ñamha arrothther ñetho' akthañtatse'th ñethpa' arro'ch yexhena apellchas pa'xhonaro allotho'chña mosyenan acheñpa' awo'chxho' kotherranet awo'chxho' emóthe'terraneta' pa'pakllo atthekmo'ch pena ñeth arro'thther aspañ pamtharrñapa' awo' ánaso'tnenap ñamha tho' palltasareñ allempoñapa' e'ño' exhe' me'chaso'twan powaser awo'ch a'pechma'terrapa' awo' e'man arrothther awo' rrothetnenerr ñañapa' año' choterr poekañthretholl allo'tsen po'shwallmerpa' awo'xho' materra papakllo awo' xherrpa' awo'xho a'paxhe'twerran po'kanothpa' awo'xho' wankanatwerran ópeller nanak womenk awo' xhotan pomarratpa' awo'xho e'yáte' ópellrroth

allo yellsheñecheth yatañneshañ ñamha allo pokllareteteth

wañ añemateñets peserrpare't epaph peyom ñeth phañematwa
o'ch ye'kellka aphthoteñets ñethcha' yaphtho'ch ñeth yémotene
sañema't serrparñats saph ñamha aphthoteñe'ts

yexhkatyeñets ñeñth sanap añ áphthoteñets

notyesthe' o'ch moth añemateñets pekwa kellek ñethcha' phañemat
awo' oterrerr kornesha' oterrnerr
yépate ayothemtanoth tsó apa' enenana
o'ch yetma'ntat ñeth pacheñer kellek atthenath
yañema't kellko attho kowampenet berroxhno
escha' kellkar phañema't
eso't photen ñeth penten all atman'tatareth
petsotsa ñoñets ñeth phañematwa añ kellko
phap popsheñeñ ñamha o'ch eñora
yá ñeñthey korretsa the'pa' esomare't amá yepnaseno
allempó yeserrpare'twa
errponmetholleshat
pékellkoñ pa'so'cheñ sekwa'yerr sekllek sanápnom a'phtho'téñtsoxhno
so'chñets awathnaneshañ nombre ancestral yanesha' chare' ñethpa' o'th tama omamerr asollare' poe'cheshem nanakcha' ama'toxhen
phañema't koñeth kellek allothpa' phanap aphthoteñets
allempo yemre'chen yéchepo amapa' yelleka'no
o'ch yekellka' kellek eche'xharr ñeñth yellkatene' ya'netsro

añthe' satsrre'matene' no'knar och napota'moeñ awo'xho' athmoekonñapa' xhepa'toch temetapa' awo wapore'ch a'yo xhen a'potatho épayo' che'tatseteret attheñapa' awo atserrteyeset poekotem
allempo yéño'sena ñerra'm xho yatsna'ten ño'srexhen
eñalletena ñamha pa'namen kenkewashexhno ñethpa'xho' atthekma eñall ñethekop yesherbhateñ tharraña atthoch senoñtá oñothpa' xhoch sethoretena mapamoet atthoch yatsepha epexhno ñamha kenkewashexhno
erratseñcha' serrparñats pekellka
errothencha yapxha
awo'xho' xhoreterran poeyochrenesha' awo'xho' checherran poepenkra'ts mataresharrmor mápoetasharrmor épayo' yowareta matar
amách yokshame'tenapa o'ch yenamoeñ llesens kornesha ñach yapoe llesens allempo o'ch yokshameta ñamha xho'ch yone kones rekërkanets attho'ch kowencha emorrta allempo yathóreñ e'nech kowen yapoeñ ora yemorreña ateth nanerrnay yatañnesha allempo amá kollaweneta añ patsro
allempó yeponpenpá añcha' yeyerpoena yáto' partsesha' ñach yenamoen athoch athoronay yenaremh ñeth ponets añekop yepeñ atthoch yeparasyosoteñ attho apoeney yokrra'mh ñethcha' yerren
pekellka ñethara serrparñats allempo o'ch pho'ch ayxhatañ erra'the pepantayesnoma o'ch o'tyeseph
awoch enamoeñet lleseñs parets atthoch chetet ñeth pathorar narmets
photyes pasocheñ ñethcha' yeñot añmho
añpa' ateth ñerra'm arrothe'tañ tharraña koñe'thpora
amá échenano chenameth tharraña a'potaso'tyen ñerra'm oño'tseneypa' xhach othátey
eso'marthe' esthe' yeperr atthoch ama wanerro kak
attheñapa' awo' morreñcha kok awo' yexhach attho es a'rrothrexha'toñ poegor atthoch chetamhpes poemoshnañ allempótheñpa' ñeth yamotspa' ñerra'm sen goatspa' xhokmo'ch rremoenan pa'namen ñeth moenen alloch shotatenan pakñethar ñamha pamo'tsesha' nésochena
wañ eñotatey ñeth ora yotwanom
penayes eñot arr apkometho ateth oxhtena ñethcha' pet
esthe oteney thó errathe' yexhena thó thépa ateth serrparetatey thépa' eñall ñamha atthoch amá' noktapechena ñethcha' yekellka
aso'chañ ñethpa' so'chene ora allpon yenten
páthe'tets potellemh tsa'tena soles anapoets
esesha't xha'nets
phaphthot eso'marthe' petso'tse
thepá' pekellkërr ñeth palltetsa poktato
yapxha e'pay yeyom allempo o'ch yeneñ poesheñarr ñach phatsa nerra'm ayxhatañ ñethcha' yekwampse allempo
setpa' ateth rranarena toch ateth thekorena ma'yarr ateth momtena wakesh ñamha wáwtena ochek ayxhatañpa' o'ch áyapaxha'yesanet amnare'tets atthoch meshanna'tet esesha'ch rranatsa womek all topoenet ma'yar ñethchaxho' meshats
neñth poeñóteñ pete'thpa' xhoch yexhateñet pakñethar atthoch amach chenkëno ama't awáthaña
koxhnesharech potsen xhop ateshapoterr yaneshllomh
yexhena mapyo amha'ten mapyo rren mapyo shótena ñamha mapyo
rrekna'teñets
errpona't pa'nameñ kakaxhno pechme'ten
parrothña pa'so'moepa' awo kothanemh a'nosetana poepepener porrorrñapa' setso' poeshpa to'ttena shonte' acheñ rranampsosanet allepa'toch mamawet
oten apá ñerra'm sherbesotwetpa' o'ch koshame'ta asheñorraré ñamha koyanesharé e'ñech arepenet
thepa' o'ch nápoerreph pátherr peyaparpa' amach phowapatsterro tharro'mar o' shonte' pemtsanaton nayara anapoerer
pechta' páthe'tets berr all órrtena par
ateth amá pekellka' arr ñeñth phanap
awathpa allempo amá waxherra okanesha shonte' pa'namen palltetethe thepa akophotheñ wañwerr berroxhno ñamha othexhno poetsatho amat yellapen anorrets all yeporeten poerraremh ñatopa all yeporeten porrayo amách es wapatso atthach yottatena ñerra'm nanak moshnañtsoy

othexhno allo'ch yamotsesha

alloth peñora womenk

pha'ñema't ñamha pekellkë' péya' pa'tatspotholl
eso'mare't ama pewapateññañe poenep
péya pa'tatstat allotsen yanesha' poekañther
ateth yakren yopoer ach akrenan popoer ñethcha' nare't pamro
atthoch yapxha kowenpa' xho'ch yetsot yapoktatar
phápanen thacha' pátherr kak
repaso posho'llpa' pátherr berr poetsátho'marnesha' nanak echemkorrotholl
napa' añekop nekellkën o'ch ñeñótateneph arrpa' séchwenet xhop llollopa' eñótatey ñeñth yethore'tena esempó yéséchwa
pechme'tenat po'poñ koshame'tames ñeth échen po'poñ acheñenesha' ñethcha' yeyenpoe' ayxhatañ apá ñamha tho' erra't yeyexhkateñ yexhateñtsopawo
shepan ech ñamha kak a'porrarrareth
allempo yañema't phañema't kellek allempopa' o'ch alla phañemater allothpa' o'ch phanap a'phtho'teñets
rreñets a'pthareth emapa' añ yomena rreñets a'bellso'tareth
sekellkërerr ametheñtets añcha' sokthanom ateth señotwanom
o'ch peserrpare'terrer epoet peyem atthoch ñethcha' yeyempoe' ayxhatañ ñamha apá erra't yeyexhkateñ pampo
escha' yapoktatyes
eñallchá' all a'poktatenet
atma'ntat tsotsmet shonte' tsa'pat shonte' etse'th ñerra'm yeyoren pa'parexhno xhoch yomchatse'ch atthoch kowencha' parteney
xhachka' kompare nemeshaphña añetholleshaka' petkathollesha' allempoñapa' awo anáph kajore' ñerram ateth the'pa' tsapathcha' yemátamoena awathekma
yexhateñets ateth ye'nyen shota'poets sekwa' atma'ntatareth allothpa' o'ch seserrpare't
allowen ñeth yexhkëtsa áxhomentaño
pátherr orrtena ñerra'm pa'tatstat po'poñ orrtenan ñera'm ma'ptat
eso't oteñ añ abhchannatpan
po'señapa' awo' óch amo' es éntneno
yáto' partsesha' atthoch sherbhatey poeyexhkatar
esempó't yéxhkatenet ko'nes
esempó yéchme'taten ateth poesheñarr yamo'tspa' añcha' yéyxha'nmoñ erro'thenthe' ñamha pokrreña ñamha ñeñth eñóten
ya'ñemater ateth orrtena añ kellek allothpa' yokwa'yes arr kellko ñeñth ya'nematwanom
thoñ all oñen ro'kpekenkewash
o'ch péserrpare't épaph peyem allothpa' o'ch phot esthe' pemnen ñeñthcha' petma'ntat ñato' mam ñato' xhop allothpa' o'ch peyexhkát e'taklle'chamets allempopa' o'ch pe'takllechapa' o'ch petpach ateth morrechena mam époet xhop
e'ñe kowen ya'pothen ñeñth yellkatene' e'ñe paxharr ye'nen ñeñth yenamoen
poepa'ñerñapa' awo' otan tse'mana' o'ch nokthaph nach aphxha'nmoe' ñeñthcha' pená amo' moenaché o'ch kothe' yanesha pátherr yethpa' awo' awenerr poetsáthopa' chento' kothan poepa'ñer
ye'mhñoten ateth sherbeso'tete'th awath allempó yesherbeso'tenpá e'ñech awathekma yema'nena o'ch orryes ñeth yewañawa allempoña o'ch poetareswenpa' o'ch nampset poesheñarr ponmenesha' o'ch atsé párets tharromarcha kowenet atsné allothñapa' ochxho thaya orryeset ellomhreso'ten e'ñech kowen pa'ten ñethach yachawapa' o'ch thaya chetampset kajonas koshame'ta asheñorraré ñamha koyanesharé eñech arepenet
errathe' eseshathe' eso'marthe' errothenthe' wañ pena'yes o'rrerr ñamha poxh arr kellko

allothñapa
phokthape'chen all poktena

eñallthe pamonte berroxhno
escha' yéthoreta allempo yeyoren allo es yeyexhkatyen
pemo'nasheñ kellermo abell
sañemach allempo setsotsé x all paxharrtena
wapore'tateñets
eso't yexhkatyeñets pha'yen asheñorrare' eso't yexhkatyeñets pha'yen koyaneshare' eso't pa'namen ormetsoxhno eñall
o'ch péna' chópapets all kowen e'moxhtena

aso'tareth

rrankxhope'n

ese'shach kowamperre poetsarroxhno

kothaphñats yapoxhayesnom

wapa poellchech poretso

athmoeñets
páyon yetsñorr ñamha totorñerexh sherben alloch yexho'moen kashemoets totorñerexh yetsñor allempo exho'moenet kashemoets xho'ch amách attha' wallashemo peshmet añ exho'moets yetsñorr allo'ch yexhkatet tsellamets pa'namenare
o'ch yenamoeñ párets womhcheñets
ya'ñema'tnen ñamha yeyexhkatnen atma'ntat tsotsmet
pátherr athmoets ñeth ápoen topoena metro
pachorpa' eneññañ xhop ñamha theyoshke' ñerra'm yerratanetpa' o'ch manxhenet kowen
páthe'tets koshtallo eñall pe'tok
peyexhkat añexhno atma'ntat
nenanma't kellek pa'tarrer ñamha e'poxh all poktena
etseñets allaka' yarepenya a'penrrot yarepenyamoe keñyawe keñyawe keñyawe
año' tépa'nom ma'yarr jaaang xhepa'to'ch yore'tan ma'yarr awo'xho máterra
yomchatseten attho'ch kowen po'nen yenaremh

beso en la nenorrar tsotstsapatan nemonerr allempo womchach
po'xhñapa' amo'xho' ame'ñyo
sokwa añ a'ñemateñets allempo o'ch seserrparet
añpa' serets ñeth shebhphar
nanak ayeñ ontapo
yeserrpare't attho yeshomemhtena oñoth poktet senteñ attho poeñoteñ yanesha nanak sheben allempo' yexhkatenan shomemtamets

meshet atarr ñeth yexhetsa mapyo
yeyerpoera pa'cheñer serrparñats ñamha ñeth tho'rrapotetsa

ro'kpetheph
pétsotse errathe' poktena

achpa' xho a'bellen

attheñapa' awo' poesheñarramha popa'ñer tharraña ñapa' pa'llerro popocheñopa' awoxho kothenan ñamha popa'ñer o'ch pemoñetpa' arrcha' pema' arrapta'metho ñañapa' awoxho' awo' pellakasotats tenoneth

che'wach
nerra'm esempo yeyexhkaten kañtherpa' allorokmach ye'nweñ eshkënoch atthenayach ñamha ye'ñwenach
tharromar atthoch yenaretatsen
ora berroxhno yach kowamperre ora poetsarroxhno
yenat atarr kellek allempo yepoxhanom
tharraña pochoyor atthoch amach ápache poerrar ñañapa' a'nawo'thó' tamoena all tarwasen pa'ñachor xhepa'toch yo'rech chets tharromar awo' enwapnatan aspeneth awo'xho kowayesan pa'ñachor amo erraye eñche' attheñapa' awó e'mosan alló tottena shonté acheñ ñañapa' awo'xho' rranampsosan pa'ñachor

all yérroren atthoch yémet xhoch yepa'nena

oten errothenthe all
shemake o'ch aññotan popoer eñe kowen xha'ran xho'p amoso' cho'ch ñamha chech aporrarre atsnetho' allothpa' wankampes kañthro attho'ch amá rro' chollop ñeñtcha nareterr popoñ charo pamro'ñamha parantmo waxhena shonte' amá axhañe ñerra'm amá yerrmoñe po'choyor

atsepenetthe allo partenet

pekwa' atma'ntatareth phot eso't penten pathe'ttso

esokopthe' sherbeney aphthoteñets
xhoch yápoeñ poesheñarr po'nmenesha ñeth ñanom yeyexhkaten atthoch yeñwenach ñerra'm ñá ama pokteyaye o'ch yerramampes rrarets kañthro

sekwa añ atma'ntatareth

shérmoema'th so'spenanen
yápa' yéchen alló yashotyen oñoth ateth ñerra'm seperr alló yerrma'yen kak shekor tsomoph tsoph tamarro' shepe'ch ñamha meshet
eñallthé ñeth yeñotatene eñech kowen yamret
erratsen the pamothroth pokte pe'maretat
tsách o'momh poe'chor
phokwa' atma'ntatareth errothena't yeth
eseshathe' yechme'taterre pa'namen pa'parexhno
norrtatyes ñeth neñótwanem errpona't kak palltena o'ch kowen onnata eñrromets
kellé kellé ñeth échen kellé ñeth amá écheno ateth yeyexhkatnom shonte' yokwampen all yexha'yena berroxhno yexheñets yeserrpare't
eséshathe' yéchme'taterre' áspanaxhno ñamha tsachtall
tsach ñeth sochetsa themerrech
erra'theña yepháyen
phañema't añ kothaphñats
pekellka pa'socheñ atma'ntatareth
eseshathe' orrtatene añ ametheñets
thematpa' temenká awo' chechnoman poekañther chetsoneth awo' allpon chopechpa' awo'xho xhap all nanak poermho e'ño allpona serrerrpa' awo'xho kothape'ch o'ch peche pokchelletallo awo' thaya pechamochpa' xhepa'toch thom shecheph arepa'to shechpetholleyaye tamoepa'to atarr awo' chemech añepa'to po'yalloph

o'ch pekellka'yes a'poktañoñtatareth
eso't sochena ñeñth atma'ntataretho'tsen
allempopa' o'ch nanak esoyat
koyanesharepa' o'ch amrechet alloch yamra yewaser go'ñapa' ache ñéthcha' yepha' ateth o' photwa moexhkan koñape' machayotha rranareta oten
pétsotse chocró x ñeñthéchage'th tho' pétsorrampes allothpa' o'ch pechte' pa'tatstato ñeñth yápoeerre'tso' petma'ntat ateth phá yaneshaxhro allempo' écherret tso' petma'ntat ateth phá komon

errothenthe' yeyorayen arrapo

sa'netsropa' eñalle't ápexhmaxhno allo partenet
e'chenan all wañen
pasocheñ mameshach yent kellek apoktata reth
esthe' eño'tateney morreñets
escha' yepha atthoch amá shekaye pekellka' eso'marthe wañannenet
ya'ñema'ten pa'tatsmet yeyexhkatnen atma'ntat tsotsmet
thopa' añ agapna'ten po'kkar
errothe't pewena
atethña poeyxheña o kanesha sentho ñamha sapomar
all yetso'tsen sherben atthoch yeñótoxhtaten ñoñets ñeth sherbets kellko
allempo seserrparetwa setsotsé poktapho ñeth setsot allempo seserrparet
tharraña e'ñoch po'chtsóche' wapateññañ poethaporñapa' awo' otan poerrollar
thépa' phapxhat phokthapña atthoch phot ñamha ñeth eso'chaña noch tho'eñótañ erro'thencha' namo'thech ñethcha noch tho' allempo yokthapechen ñethcha yot
yañema't serrparñats ñamha yekwa all pechnaten kellek
amá yerrmoena' shotamets xhoch ñanom ye'parech ñamha xhoch yéthore'tena
eñótatenat ñeth ámethen
ateth amá amá namothtena orrtateñets xho ñanom newomchat neyemnesha
themettsen napa'xho' allo nakowenten allpon nethórra'yena
posho'llpa' xhokma chechenan pa'sme'll
allempopa' xhoch wa'ñannatet allcha' koshame'tet poksheñesha' tharromar pokte nenteñ attho koshametenet allempo a'thorenet sherbes párets attho'ch kowen achpatennay yerrartsor
atarr poénamarrém kawall
añ serrpartñatspá ateththé nokthapechnom ñano'm
photnom ñethcha' phorrtat ñanomcha pekellkë pekellkapano allothpa' o'ch phorrtach

xhop panarrmer e'chwareth
yeserrpare't attho ya'mhteññañ parets nanétsro mothtena koshamhñats añ palltétsa o'ch yapoktách errothencha yephá o'ch yenam llesens po'nanesha attho'ch yokshameta

thopa' a'matampenan amartorr

o'yosmaren xhach thepa' xha allasmaren

o'ch yeñot errathe eñalletena arrapoxhno

warota'teñets

nekellkathé otatyeñets errothenthé pa'cheñer

añpa' arr kellkëna
alló entosan popa'ñer año' chetare'ten berr rromoé moeye'tsó poksheñeshokmañen

rrenan po'tasher ach ma'mathan pa'thoñen
eso't senten arr atma'ntátaretho
arrapareth otatso
asocenapa' xha o'rrerrña'ten
phokwa'yes atma'tátareth allothpa' o'ch peyerpoerra ateth ya'koshen
the'pa o'ch yeserrpare't patherr serrpare'teñets yeyomneshakop
shonto'ña kotha'yeñ ñanmoth allempoñapa' awo' alla moenme'chyeset tharro'mar amo' awantéto seneth xhokmo'ch otenanet
oten añkaye phatene

chech allo tho' nare'tenan ma'ñorrochech chetso' ñerra'm ta'te' xho' yénare'teñ alloch yeparten éllap

eseshakpa't kellkenet

añ pokteñets echenan a'poktatareth ñethcha' yetsotat añekop sherben attho'ch yeyxha kowen ñethomarña pokté' o'ch yetsotat
sana'p a'phtho'teñets
o' poesheñattsamena po'naneshare' ñeñth etsotene' yeñoñ añexhnopa' nanak llekëñets tharromar ñeñthey yaneshaypa' ama ye'ñoranateñe ya'kñe'thar yeñoñ yepakllomar
wallama'thteñets
o' wapoena ñetho'mar sénthetnen
nethpa' naka' photen the'pa' phapoen poewetall komprechñe ñamha bes neth pórrarre' ñañapa' orrenano' asermet ñamha mapoe' tsellemh awo'xhoña asra' atthótho' a'krratan tso' allempotheño'ña écherret tso' yenyo theme'ttsówañen

pekellkayes pa'namen kellëk

eso'marthe' eñótateney
nexhopo'ten xho kothare'tenen poeshenarr llollo awo'ch yottampsan pa'pakllo

tharraña ñéth jopaxho' moetsero poesheñarr pa'llerr awo' kowe' moenpotho all rromxhat acheñenesha' allo wapa' tsapo arrorrpo alloña ené panmeto xho jojatspe' amo' kowenaye' rrananerro awo' tho' áporo'yeth poesheñarr áporo'yeth etsotane'tho morreñtsoxhno a'moen chopechen étenan oñ pechenan tsach
pamotseshañapa' xho'aphthotare'chet errathe entnerran pa'namen narmetsoxhno ñapa' awo'ch e'nereta' tharraña amo' esesha' onterraye tharromar awo' chenkërra' ñethpa' año mellañoteñ poenaremh thepa' awo' apan yanesha
pekellkayes e'paph peyom ñeth atthekma tomantayetsa
petsotsá poechenatets all poktena kellek a'poktatareth ñeth sañematwa
sanáp a'phtho'teñe'ts
poñpa' xhach so'stallllen
pátherr pareshe'mats alló monte
phañemach épaph peyom
yemhchatse'teñ llollo tero'pexh
peyexhkat atma'ntat tsotsmet phokwa'nom pa'tatstat
allempo és a'worenet napa' amá pókte' nonteno éshopoeñets
awepa'to' apnasetwanet ayots
poetsarrare sa'pomar arr anets sa'popa' all atarr chopoen shonte atsompapoxhno ñetpa amá echeneto poetsath xho' nareteñe't ora ñeth tsomyenet ñamha ñeth pomyenet popoñ anetsomar ñetpa xho' eyayenet pa'parexhno patso allo'ch ateshamerrtena ñeth tsomyenet amá pokteyaye ñeth narmetsexhno choparen atsompapoxhno atarr berr ñamha amach tama yatsnatyeno ateth phayena othexhno berroxhno ñamha ko'chexhno
thepá' yapoktateñ o'ch yenare't rekërkanets alloweney attho'ch amá yachenkache ama't errponaña

attho a'matamper mhorr po'karpach yamo'ts
moékollo'teñets
pekellka' e'ñoteñets allcha' xhapnerr takatholl
eshekthe' apartañpa' eñóte ñan ñeth eso'cha yépe' atsotena poesheñarr atsnañeth
allempo wapore'tenet pa'ñyaphoth po'rrerrña pomre'te
eswaka' masheñe pepha'yen
eso't serrpare'tatey añ kellek
amaka' mallapharoth newapateno' ech ñeñtho'marña ama nesha'tneno poenpa'ts atthoch amach eñerrto
pa'socheñ sekellka ñoñtsoxhno ñeth yetsa kellwe ñamha aspanamámoen
errothenthe' eso't sherben
esesha't nare'te' koñe'th parant
acheñ ñeth nanak go'tets
errothet orrterra totana' ch
poso'k pharrotampes atthekma eskont atma'ntatareth
esesha't kowén pentapret phá esómar' yañemat allempo o'ch yanaph
eso'marecha nañemat kellek
allothoña yeñóterr go'tats
koshepa' materra' ama't awathapa' amá poentarano ateth cheshathollmath añetholl
konaren tatste' orranrexho
pa'namenare kekaxhno ñeth eñall yenyo ñeth atarr yerren ñamha patantarrpa xho'ch yepomoeñ okësho allo'ch yeyorayen yeposor yeshtam
awo't thaya senatpa' calos
pekellkër arr chetatso ora ñeth eñotatey akellkareth
poktethe yenteñ o'ch yenamoeñ yompor párets atthó apo'nennay yenaremh
sapa' soktharet sachor all yorenan teropexh
yechokré all poktena a'phthó'teñets eschá' yepha atthoch yetsotat apoktateñets
nanak natsotna neklle' atsnom womenk amá nawanto o'ch nómacha patso nanakcha' kowen ontennet ñerra'm xhara'net
yapa' xha ya'mñecheña rremosheñ yemneñ phach pampoe' añeñpo ekothena'pa' ño' allsensareth atthoch ama ya'rromñathtenañe
eso't phokthapechen phá pekellkë arr
peye' oth ñeth anetsa xho'pmo
eso't rrarets rrenet ora acheñenesha' errothena't yema'teñet phamo'tsesha' penyo
añcha' yena pa'socheñ ñethcha' yorrtat
wapmocha' arr oñem poetsatho o'ch wapatan pa'parexhno posholl
ama't atethpa' o' peyxhe' go'tats the'pa' phach yexhaterre' phamo'tsesha' ñamha the'pa' o'ch peyetá tharro'mar ñeñth pemtsa porrayopa' ñeñthpa' nompor ñapa' achñerrcha' o'xha' po'poñ pontach ñamha petháporpa' o' a'methampsey ñeñtho' otwapa' awo' so'tneñ allo' chenkena
péna eñot ateth oxhtenena kellëk
enamoenan etsoterr o'ch wapá atthoch yexhatan cheshanesha' ateth nare'tatsetenet
atthoch pena' parrochñapa' awo'xho' kothe' pa'so'moe a'yoth allo entosa pa'ñachor xho tsorrotenan po'chets
esempothe' a'bellenet
alló shomemtenet ateth ñerra'm
añ yoten mákall choch ñeth yénare'ten ñethpa' arrapo' llollopa' tesenan mákall o'ch a'nane
awáthekmach setántena se'yátena kellpachó atthoch amach wepotheñ sémo'këno ñamha eshkënoch a'nosensa chellpe chellpe atthothpa' se'noñtenach
yanapyes añ aphthoteñets ñeth yañema'twa

llollopa' nanak a'koshañ masato
senmake'cheñets
poktenathe o'ch yayaterra berr

pa'tarrer pátherr tsachtat
po'ñoxhthe' shépa' añ poenaserrtsa acheñ all serrparñatso ñeñth yeñótatene' añpa' attha ye'moe' ama yentarepa' ñeñthpa' o' ñamha awo'xho' ateth mothtena
pekwa' all aynatareth ya'netser po'mapa pot
errothenthé yeñotyerr atthoch yanpayes ñamha eso'thé yanpayes

esesha't ateth petsa
koyanesha'pa' esthe' penan añ shé shepshesha' ema' shepshesha'pa' esthe' penan añ koyanesha' shé ema' a'phtho'teñets
ora pa'namen ñeth che'cheptallma'thexhno
phokwatyes all poermho poetsatho shonte' poerraremh all rren ashath ñamha ro'këph
allempo ama sañemateñapa' yapthotas
añ eñotateñets añ sochena attho ashanenkanesha yempannena pekellka patats' kothaphñats ñeth peñosertena ñethcha' eñótatey añ eñotateñets

errponthe' eñall
sekwa'yerr sékllek sanapnom ñoñtsoxhno
eso't phayen pathetets acheñ eso'marthe' yañema'ten añ atma'ntatareth
esesha'tña nanak awamenkath ñamha a'pnasañ ñerra'm phach pamo'mte' cheshanesha' ñeñth a'pnasetwet errothena'tcha' kothapechataph
thépa' peyo'che patherr ñethcha' pekellka kellek yexhateñe'ts pekellkató erro'thenat yeyexhkaten photasher
o'ch otnom errathe' shontena esokmañen
emanerra ma'yarrpa' nanako parasyosotan posholl ñamha posomoe ro' këph allempoñapa' awo' koshametarsa allowen berroxhno

watamhphseñets

nameñatthe' ñeth notyes
errponthe' kg xhop échen the' echenaneñ ápan ach échen the' anapoets
wayollpa' rrosan pañ parroser
errothenách yépe
esoch yaynatoñ pa'so'chen a'metheñets
añeñpopa' pokte'the' o'ch yeporetasotyes poretspa' allo ye'potampeña berroxhno ñamha othexhno atthoch amá entenyé añcha' ye'nen ñeñth yemnen ñamha xhoch yemhchatse'ch payomph atthoch ama es ya'mhteno
añ ñenth achets ochek achap toponeth
esthe' palltetsa o'ch yeyexhkat yechopap
newa pena'yes phamha
allempoña e'nwan acheñpa' poyorñotho' paya'ta ñamha acheñpa' poyorñotho' paya'ta ñamha añethollamha poeyochpa' lleka
awath yanehsapa' moéxhkane'th aser atthoch yexhkatan kochell
pekellka ateth sherbeso'tenet
ateth ama poetakrespa' e'ñe kowen anareth all poktena
páthetets apxheñe'ts o'ch kothapechet errothencha chemnatet ñeth rromayeset
errponthe' eñerr xhop ápa'nom pampacocha époet palma
peserrpare'tach ayxhatañ añ serrparñatspa ñeth yokthapechnom ñanom
thekma mátwerra chésha' awepa't yóre'ch shécheph
eñóteñe'ts yokwampen kakaxhno esthé phayen yamotsesha arr atma'ntataretho
phokwa'nom ñamha pha'ñema'tnom pa'tatsmet
o'ch semñoten eñe mocheth poeserrparña seyom
yapñapa' e'ño mamesha matapa' awo poktan tomepa' awoxho alla serrpare'tet thematenpa' awo'xho alla oterrer
the'pa' o'ch álla sokwa'yererr sekllek o'ch petsotsa poktepho all pokten ñato korsapho x all ama pokteyaye
eso'mare't yekellkë eseshat kellkayese a'metheñets
kanoth awath yapa' cheshotheñ yerrma yechopap ateth yencheth yatañ ñamha yomporeñ yechopappa' ñeth chópapets eñall ñerra'm añ yomnen chópapets eñall ñerra'm añ yomene o'ch yomtsa othexhno año'ch yeneñ cha'parro attheña ñerra'm añ yomnen berr atesha' año'ch yeneñ etsethó ñamha panmeto ñamha atthoch es yenén xho'ch ñanom yentotáta anarrmho ñamha parantacho' ñamha yetseth aññapa' panmetpa' año yeyexhkateñ monkno
erratsena't atma'ntat ñeth penten sochena tsotsa'ne' epphatenoneth
pekellka apoktatareth ñoñets año atma'ntataretho' yekellkën attho yéthore'tena allempo yashotayen poetsathoth yañenaten ñamha yekellkën
yekellka errothenthé naretatsen yanesha ñamha ateth naretenan poxhopoer senthephnomarnesha
chech chech arrorrr thopep kañther arrorr kaka'm kochell árrorr kochell tate' arrorr tate' tate' thopep chech kaka'm kakam thopep thopep kochell chech tate' kaka'm petsotsampes pa'socheñ atma'ntatareth
es yámothetpa' xhoch ye'nweñ nanak sherben allempó es yámothtenpa' xhoch ya'poeñ allochñapa' attach a'thoray yáto' parets popocheño es yeyexhkaterrerrpa' e'ñech kowen ye'nwererr
e'ñe poemoereñoth wathrenapa' eñótatey errothencha' ya'tarwasañterra atthoch ama yemoeroxhterro yachporrñoth

ese'shat phayene' erróthenthé phayeñe't

porroxhér
nárrolle'ten shécheph mapyo
o'ch ya'ñematwa orrtateñets épsheña cheshá óch napa nokthapechen allowen acheñenesha xho'ch orrtatet arrápo poetsathoth attho'ch amá napa nomneñ ora acheñenesha xho'ch yexhkatet arrápo ateth yápaxho cheshaneshay yentaterrcha yamha narmets poetsathomar ñeth échen yanesha
thekoreñets
pa'llo yéch wallama'th yoten shonte' pa'llo tho'tall

añ kellëkpa' oteney
allempopa' o'ch ñethamha yeyxhá ñerra'm ateth yephapa' nanakcha' yemxhare'tena
allempo'sherbe'sotenet ora acheñeneshapa' e'ñech mamthoth thomyenet ñerra'm sherbe'sotwapa' o'chxho' thaya erreta orrothes poemharrcha' apet koyaneshare ñamha asheñorrare' allempochña thaya onachet ora ñeth allo'tsa'yen e'nech e'nweñet atthoch rrallmechet

takratspeñets

ayemañeth
napa o'ch nekellka kellek yexhateñe'ts añekop
yeserrpare't ateth yomchatse't allempo yeyexhkaten pa'namen shotamets so'kwayes añ a'tmanta'tareth allothpa' seserrpare't
ayxhatañpa' o'ch otan cheshanesha' e'ñech e'mhñotet e'ñe kowen atthoch eñóchet o'ch yeyellsheñe'ch pa'namen ñeth yexhen yanesha' o'ch yotanet arro'tsen paya'th kañther tarramets allcha yemata esempo peñotnom erponthe atsetara eñall esthe aspan peshtenallempopa ochpeñot amnar atsetara

seyerpoerra ñeñth eñótatwas po'nanesha' erra'tsenthe' yeñótatene' all enall ápexhexhno ñamha chemoer
petsotsa koñeth serrparñats ñeth kowen pent kellko eso'marthe' kowen pench
yeserrpare't attho yokwa'yen all po'nyen arraepoxhno sapxhena epsheñatets
peyerpoera ñeth serrpare'tatas eñótañ ñamha pha'ñema't pa'socheñ kellek phokwa' tema'nteñe'ts allothpa' péserrpare't

womenkna'ntateñets
pekellka ateth yéthóre'tena allempo yepartena
ya'ñemater ateth órrtena añ kellek allothpa' yokwa'yes arr kellko ñeth ya'ñematwanom

emapa' moéntakatha chope'chen
errothenthe' yemhchatseteñ llesens yáto' partsesha' e'ñé peso'chñothpa' o'ch yexhore'teñ wathrena' atthochpa' o'the yenpa'teney poeyochresha' añe yethro o'ch yétanmaso'ta'moen atthothpa' thekmathe' ye'nwen yetar
yoten ñeth xhayemettsa koweney
womchateñets yesoterra errothenat añ kellëk
añ poktetsa o'ch yenaretyerr pa'namen pa'parexhno ñamha o'ch yokwamperr poetsath attho'ch amá yechenkërro allo' yeparteyena ñamha xho'ch pha'ñema't kellek allothpa' phanap aphtho'teñe'ts
añ serrparñatspa' eñótateney atthoch yemcha'na'ch koyanesha' ñeñth arrollareth

oten errathe' all
arr yanetsro nanák sherbeney a'metheñets ñethcha' yephayes
poérexh poérexh ma'llamechpa' nanak échar
allempo yepoxhwe patherr kellek epoxhe yénen epoxhallowa' wañen kellek
sapaxharrterr ñeñth sekellkawa' ñeñth yepha'yes ateth amá kowena't sekellka'nom a'metheñets
o'ch yot awen chetso mameshach newerra
atthó órrta tso' yenyo awath yatañneshañpa' amo' échete'the tso' alloch poetare'tet año' échaye'th tso' kommana' attho'ch po'tsom ñétho'marña allempopa' e'ñoch ochtapa' awo'chxho alla añyanatwerrana po'tsom
o'ch yekwa'yes all kowen pats ñamha all allametets eñall o'ñ ñanom ñerra'm amá yeyexhkatena sa'p
